{"tid":275290,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"識Leave Thursday","createTime":"2017-06-08T02:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T02:25:08.000Z","uid":36148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c4387c3c5397a56f2403c6d1e1f30d8fe8109b8f","tid":275290,"uid":36148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:13:45.000Z","msg":"今日晨早由夢中醒咗，感覺到腳板底痕，腦海彈出一個要去睇醫生的諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後個人遊魂咁行咗去樓下商場睇醫生(估唔到有診所開咁早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。入去登記後就直入見醫生。佢問我咩事，我答佢腳板底痕唔想返工，跟住佢笑咗一笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用枝雪條棍隊我喉嚨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />再用聽筒探我背脊聽下呼吸就話我感冒，出去等拎3日藥同休息一日。姑娘俾咗3日藥我再收我$360<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家在屋企打緊GTA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55308a56db5261bb7179ed1f1a67d9f89a5b83b","tid":275290,"uid":103242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:25:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.yes-news.com/201509/nzeK3ltq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.yes-news.com%2F201509%2FnzeK3ltq.jpg&h=9fe36fb0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}